Why Pipeline is required ?? 
Important Points of Pipeline:

Pipeline basically needs a basic understanding of groovy language
In General jenkins Jobs, Plugins required but in Pipeline no need to install multiple plugins for execution
In Normal jenkins jobs, error tracing is quite time taking and challenging part but in Pipeline error tracing is quite simple
In Pipeline we split the code into stages which helps us to trace the code errors easily
In Pipeline maintaining the code is easy
